These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, golf, swimming, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, firefighter, water-polocher, dressmaker
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is soccer and the firefighter##2
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is soccer##7
4. the firefighter is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the water-polocher##1
6. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | swimming | water-polo       | golf | soccer        |
| Job      | water-polocher  | firefighter | dressmaker        | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: lemon, grapefruit, watermelon, spinach
1. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person drinking milk##7
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person eating spinach is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage     | milk | mirinda       | tea         | coffee     |
| Food   | grapefruit   | spinach | watermelon | lemon |

