.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
City: new-york, colone, hannover, liverpool
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, fonseca, chaman
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##7
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the person traveling to colone##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| City   | colone | liverpool | hannover | new-york  |
| Cigar   | fonseca | tiparillo  | chaman   | ritmeester |

