.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
House: cape-cod, wooden, futuristic, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, coach, bartender, writer
1. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the coach and the gothic-revival house##7
3. the futuristic house is the writer##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the writer##1
5. the wooden house is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| House   | wooden | cape-cod | gothic-revival       | futuristic |
| Job   | coach      | librarian   | bartender | writer  |

