.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, musical, spy
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, bridge, go
1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person playing go is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching adventure movies##7
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
7. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | adventure   | spy | crime |
| Game   | backgammon      | domino | go      | bridge |

