6. the chef is somewhere between the project-manager and the firefighter##7
7. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar      | prince | bluemaster      | havana | chaman     |
| Job   | project-manager    | chef | firefighter   | nurse |

