.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hedgehog, fish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the fish is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the owner of the hedgehog##7
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Pet       | fish | cat | guinea-pig | hedgehog |
| Birthday   | november   | january      | september        | march  |

