3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
7. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Color      | fuchsia   | grey | yellow | ivory   |
| Transport   | taxi | jet-ski   | helicopter | boat |

