There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, mauve, yellow, azure
1. the person playing go is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person playing billiard##7
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Game         | billiard    | go | poker     | mah-jongg |
| Color   | yellow | azure  | mauve | apricot |

 